@page "/fill"

<div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24">
    <section class="py-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">Image Fill Modes</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            The versatile <code class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 font-mono px-2 py-1 rounded">Fill</code> prop empowers images to seamlessly adapt to the dimensions of their parent container. Explore the different ways an image can fill its space, crucial for crafting responsive and visually engaging layouts.
        </p>

        <div class="rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-t-lg">Full Width Fill (object-cover)</h2>
            <div class="relative aspect-video bg-gray-100">
                <Image Src="/images/white-horse.jpg"
                       Alt="Fill image with object-cover"
                       Fill="true"
                       CssClass="object-cover"
                       Priority="true" />

            </div>
            <p class="p-4 text-sm text-gray-600">
                The image elegantly fills the entire container, maintaining its aspect ratio while ensuring no empty spaces. Cropping may occur to fit the dimensions.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div class="rounded-lg shadow-md ">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-t-lg">Fill with <code class="font-mono">object-cover</code></h2>
                <div class="relative aspect-video   ">
                    <Image Src="/images/white-horse.jpg"
                           Alt="Fill image with object-cover"
                           Fill="true"
                           CssClass="object-cover h-full w-full"
                           Priority="true" />
                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-t-lg">Fill with <code class="font-mono">object-contain</code></h2>
                <div class="relative aspect-video   ">
                    <Image Src="/images/white-horse.jpg"
                           Alt="Fill image with object-contain"
                           Fill="true"
                           CssClass="rounded-md object-contain h-full w-full"
                           Priority="true" />
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 rounded-md bg-gray-100 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Code Example</h3>
            <pre class="bg-gray-200 rounded-md overflow-x-auto p-4 font-mono text-sm text-gray-900"><code>
&lt;div class="container"&gt; &lt;!-- Define a container with desired dimensions --&gt;
    &lt;Image Src="/hero-image.jpg"
           Alt="Fill mode image"
           Fill="true" /&gt; &lt;!-- Enable fill mode --&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</code></pre>
        </div>
    </section>
</div> 